            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-10888.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from Ernst Krause, 11 March 1877</ref>, and <ref target="./DCP-LETT-10912.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to Ernst Krause, 25 March 1877</ref>.</note>
